Bgs testS
  u64x2 a
  u64x2 b
  b128 x
  b128 y
  b128 z1
	b128 z2
	b128 z3
	b128 z4
	b128 z5
	b128 z6
	b128 z7
Ens

Fnc test
  Idw a, 0, 0x1234567890ABCDEF
  Idw a, 1, 0x0120148439542F29
  
  Idw b, 0, 0x82FBA38A0134FEDE
  Idw b, 1, 0x010F88BCF4ED8012

  Xb128 x, a
  Xb128 y, b

	And z1, x, y
	Or z2, x, y
	Xor z3, x, y
	Andnot z4, x, y
	Not z5, x
  
  ShiftLeft z6, x, 10
  ShiftRight z7, x, 10
  
Ret

























